patthana9.9:4.1: Hetuyā tīṇi, ārammaṇe ekaṃ …pe… avigate tīṇi.
patthana9.9:5.1: Nasappaṭighaṃ nakusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca …pe… naappaṭighaṃ nakusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca …. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
patthana9.9:6.1: Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe ekaṃ …pe… aññamaññe cha …pe… avigate nava.
patthana9.9:7.1: Narūpiṃ nakusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca …pe… naarūpiṃ nakusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca …. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
patthana9.9:8.1: Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe tīṇi, adhipatiyā pañca …pe… aññamaññe cha …pe… purejāte āsevane ekaṃ …pe… avigate nava.
patthana9.9:9.1: Nalokiyaṃ nakusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca …pe… nalokuttaraṃ nakusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca …. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
patthana9.9:10.1: Hetuyā pañca, ārammaṇe dve …pe… āsevane ekaṃ …pe… avigate pañca.
patthana9.9:11.1: Nakenaci viññeyyaṃ nakusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca …pe… nanakenaci viññeyyaṃ nakusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca …. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
